Class AstTransformationNode

AstTransformationNode is the base type that is used for all SQL Server Integration Services dataflow transformations/components in Biml.

RemoveInput(AstDataflowInputPathNode)

This method will unwire the specified inputPath on this transformation. This may require deleting the input path, mapping it to the DeadOutputPath, or even adding a new InputPath connected to the DeadInputPath, depending on the surrounding dataflow. The method handles all of the intricacies of managing implicit input path, without any further intervention from the caller.
